thread.title_full: SJF Material Handling Inc. reviewed by Ken Bjork

author: Ken Bjork
title: Ken Bjork
text: I worked with Vance and Material Handlers on an time sensitive special order for some large conveyors. Vance was excellent with every step of the order and delivery. Vance and Material Handlers was exceptionally responsive and was willing to work with us on our special order. I would recommend Material Handlers.
